<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>New Insurance Quote Submitted</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      color: #333;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: auto;
      padding: 2rem;
      background: #f9f9f9;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }
    .title {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .info {
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .referral-link {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background-color: #06213d;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
    }
    .footer {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #777;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="title">New Insurance Quote Submission</div>
    <div class="info">
      <p><strong>Name:</strong> {{name}}</p>
      <p><strong>Quote ID:</strong> {{quoteId}}</p>
    </div>

    <p>Attached is the full insurance quote submitted by the client in PDF format.</p>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>This is an automated email sent from your insurance portal.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
